Class SynthPartCredits

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epoch.evals.impl.chemEvals.synthEvals.SynthPartCredits
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ChemConstants, MechSynthConstants, FormatConstants, SynthPartCreditsConstants, SynthConstants
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SynthScheme, SynthSelective

    public class SynthPartCredits
extends Object
implements SynthPartCreditsConstants
    Superclass for SynthScheme and SynthSelective, allowing partial credit for certain kinds of incorrect responses.
